HEADWORD: Incrassative
<hw>In*cras"sa*tive</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Having the
quality of thickening; tending to thicken.</def>
<rj><au>Harvey.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Incrassative</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Incrassative
<hw>In*cras"sa*tive</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A substance which has the
power to thicken; formerly, a medicine supposed to thicken the
humors.</def> <rj><au>Harvey.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Increasable</ent>⟦br⟧
